      "name": "build-loop",
      "description": "Multi-phase build orchestration with integrated debugging: assess, plan, execute, review, iterate. Plan-verify gate on Phase 2 (with security rules). Phase 4-A build-time security review (OWASP LLM/Agentic Top 10 + MITRE ATLAS) when riskSurfaceChange triggers. DOE-first multi-factor optimization with autoresearch baseline handoff. Optional UI design gates. Bundled debug-loop, debugging-memory, logging-tracer, security-methodology, defenseclaw-bridge skills + MCP incident-memory server (renamed `build-loop-debugger` to coexist with standalone claude-code-debugger).",
      "version": "0.9.0",
      "author": {
        "name": "Tyrone Ross"
